articles.title: Russell expecting Aston Martin to be ‘really strong’ at Australian GP as he counters recent Hamilton set-up comments - Formula 1
articles.description: George Russell has tipped Aston Martin to be an even stronger force at the Australian Grand Prix, pointing to the impressive cornering ability the AMR23 has displayed over the first two rounds of the season.
